      <a class="block px-4 py-3 rounded-xl text-base font-medium text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 hover:text-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-50 dark:hover:bg-gray-900 transition-colors" href="/profile">Trilha de Aprendizado</a>
